Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給你做了法式吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  陽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是資源垃圾回收的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得把瓶瓶罐罐都扔出去喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定記住喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:52.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好困
